text: Gymnothorax dorsalis is a moray eel found in the western Pacific Ocean, around Hong Kong, Malacca, Malaysia, and Taiwan.Gymnothorax dorsalis at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Seale in 1917. ==References== dorsalis Category:Fish described in 1917 Category:Taxa named by Alvin Seale
